      "surface": {
        "jp": "PKI (Public Key Infrastructure：公開鍵基盤)",
        "zh": "公钥基础设施（PKI）",
        "en": "PKI (Public Key Infrastructure)"
      },
      "definition": {
        "jp": "公開鍵暗号方式やデジタル署名で使用する公開鍵の持ち主を保証するためのインフラ（基盤）。公開鍵の正当性を認証局に保証してもらう仕組み。",
        "zh": "用于保证公钥加密方式及数字签名中所使用公钥归属者身份的基础设施。通过认证机构（CA）来保证公钥正当性的机制。",
        "en": "An infrastructure (foundation) for guaranteeing the owner of a public key used in public key cryptography and digital signatures. A mechanism in which the Certificate Authority (CA) vouches for the legitimacy of public keys."
      },
      "kana_helper": null
    },
